{"tid":1856941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟向中國運12噸防護裝備","createTime":"2020-02-02T02:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T07:51:55.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":563,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"0afb4c688eff0dd0998a10da273fc6589aee288a","tid":1856941,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:21:46.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒疫情持續，內地醫療物資緊缺。歐盟昨（1日）表示，各成員國已調動12噸防護裝備運往中國，以協助中方遏制疫情；中國駐歐盟使團今（2日）回應稱，中方表示衷心感謝。<br />\n<br />\n中國國務院總理李克強昨與歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩通話，李克強提到當前正全力保障醫護人員所需的醫療物資，也希望歐盟為中方通過商業渠道從歐盟成員國緊急採購醫療物資提供必要便利。"},{"pid":"6ca0335613ca2f84f3dd5caa1bf038a3d219f18f","tid":1856941,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20200202/s00004/1580607254154/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20200202%2Fs00004%2F1580607254154%2F&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=a970e479\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20200202%2Fs00004%2F1580607254154%2F&h=d9f60f3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20200202/s00004/1580607254154/</a>"},{"pid":"ec783b78284a757300f6ae2d7552ad49e256f1c2","tid":1856941,"uid":194326,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:22:35.000Z","msg":"好快唔見"},{"pid":"f51664e484647f74f04d62773f581b471e3cbb9c","tid":1856941,"uid":259010,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:23:12.000Z","msg":"咪又俾紅十扲黎賣"},{"pid":"05b3c41da89e367d57998e01365e6077cd93d3f0","tid":1856941,"uid":88743,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NwWoAIZZGTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNwWoAIZZGTA&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=38a0f522\" tar